BA_CONCRETE

:Credits:
dev: boost

:Details:
ba_ stands for the battle arena map type.
This map is intended for 3v3, but can be used with less people.

:Tools:
source sdk



****please do not rip this map in any way shape or form****



:::::Instructions:::::

1. Extract map to C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\youraccountnamehere\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
2. Run Counter Strike: Source
3. Have fun.

-boost
